Difference variables

Delta_vars.Rd

This is the list of difference variables of the form Delta_var_stage, where var is the variable name (from ReboundTools::key_analysis_vars) and stage is the rebound stage being considered (from ReboundTools::rebound_stages).

Delta_vars

Format

A string list with 48 entries.

Delta_eta_star

Calculated as eta_star - eta_orig.

Delta_p_s_star

Calculated as p_s_star - p_s_orig.

.

Etc.

.

Etc.

.

Etc.

Delta_M_dot_tilde

Calculated as M_dot_tilde - M_dot_bar.

Delta_N_dot_tilde

Calculated as N_dot_tilde - N_dot_bar.
